* 5703 Hevelius, asteroid
* List of largest optical telescopes historically
* IH Cassiopeiae, a star designation used with some frequency, from his star map
* Heweliusz, a Polish optical astronomy satellite launched in 2014 as part of the Bright-star Target Explorer (BRITE) programme

